29
00:01:36.950 --> 00:01:41.500
Roger and Whitebeard

30
00:01:39.370 --> 00:01:41.500
The baby is finally here!

31
00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:42.500
Tamago!

32
00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:43.500
Konbu!

33
00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:44.500
Chikuwa!

34
00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:45.420
Tsukune!

35
00:01:46.130 --> 00:01:49.340
Hey, knock it off! He's a baby,
not a pot of oden!

36
00:01:50.090 --> 00:01:51.880
This is our first child!

37
00:01:52.550 --> 00:01:54.590
The name I give you means peerless...

38
00:01:56.300 --> 00:01:59.970
You shall be called Kozuki Momonosuke!

39
00:02:03.020 --> 00:02:05.730
Lord Oden, they have issued
wanted posters for you.

40
00:02:06.150 --> 00:02:09.530
I am afraid you are now
a fully-fledged outlaw overseas.

41
00:02:09.530 --> 00:02:12.150
For Lady Toki and Lord Momonosuke's safety,

42
00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:15.910
perhaps you should consider
returning to Wano.

43
00:02:15.910 --> 00:02:19.410
Not yet, Izo! I have yet to find my answer!

44
00:02:19.410 --> 00:02:22.750
We will be fine. Do not worry!

45
00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:25.330
This thing may be called a newspaper,

46
00:02:25.330 --> 00:02:29.000
but there's no news about Wano in it!

47
00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:33.510
Well, just like Zou, they have no method
of sending info outside the country.

48
00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:36.550
I wonder meow Kin
and the others are doing?

49
00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:43.600
What?!

50
00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.310
You are appointing commanders?!

51
00:02:45.310 --> 00:02:47.360
Our crew keeps on growing.

52
00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:51.820
How do you feel about
splitting into five or so divisions?

53
00:02:51.820 --> 00:02:54.570
That's a great idea, Pops!

54
00:02:54.570 --> 00:02:56.660
I wanna be a commander!

55
00:02:56.660 --> 00:02:58.200
Me, too!

56
00:02:58.200 --> 00:02:59.660
Oden!

57
00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:02.450
You will lead the second division!

58
00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:07.250
Well... Um... Uh... Um...

59
00:03:09.090 --> 00:03:09.960
Just do it!

60
00:03:11.590 --> 00:03:15.840
Newcomers would join the crew
from time to time, much like we had...

61
00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.050
Listen!

62
00:03:17.050 --> 00:03:19.720
This ain't no fishing boat! We're pirates!

63
00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:21.560
P-Please!

64
00:03:22.140 --> 00:03:24.310
I've got nowhere else to go!

65
00:03:24.310 --> 00:03:26.270
Hey, knock it off!

66
00:03:26.270 --> 00:03:27.480
What's your name?

67
00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:31.110
Teach!

68
00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.950
Very well.

69
00:03:36.950 --> 00:03:38.110
Come aboard!

70
00:03:40.700 --> 00:03:42.700
Thank you so much!

71
00:03:44.410 --> 00:03:47.330
Another orphan it would seem...

72
00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:50.630
Did you see that?

73
00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:52.590
Something just flew past us!

74
00:03:54.090 --> 00:03:57.630
No matter how far I sail,
my curiosity is never satiated!

75
00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.510
Commander!

76
00:03:59.510 --> 00:04:01.890
We need to scout the area first!

77
00:04:02.260 --> 00:04:06.270
I do not know how to end such an adventure!

78
00:04:07.600 --> 00:04:10.810
Meanwhile, in Wano...

79
00:04:10.810 --> 00:04:12.480
Extra, extra!

80
00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:14.150
Read all about it!

81
00:04:14.150 --> 00:04:18.910
The shogun, Lord Sukiyaki,
is in critical condition!

82
00:04:18.910 --> 00:04:20.410
Lord Sukiyaki!

83
00:04:20.410 --> 00:04:22.620
Within Wano's borders...

84
00:04:23.410 --> 00:04:29.370
a grave matter brought the daimyo
of each region to the Flower Capital.

85
00:04:32.130 --> 00:04:34.630
I wish for Oden...

86
00:04:35.250 --> 00:04:37.510
to succeed me as shogun.

87
00:04:37.510 --> 00:04:40.430
Of course, Lord Sukiyaki!

88
00:04:42.220 --> 00:04:46.100
But seeing as Oden is abroad at the moment,

89
00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:51.400
it appears I must appoint
a proxy in his absence...

90
00:04:52.150 --> 00:04:54.820
in the event anything should befall me.

91
00:04:56.320 --> 00:05:01.110
I have chosen the man Oden cared for
as though he were his younger brother...

92
00:05:01.110 --> 00:05:03.160
Kurozumi Orochi!

93
00:05:06.120 --> 00:05:07.910
Orochi?

94
00:05:08.540 --> 00:05:09.870
What are you doing here?

95
00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:15.210
Oden cared for him as though
he were his younger brother?

96
00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:16.880
Is that true?

97
00:05:18.300 --> 00:05:23.050
Thank you for allowing me to atone for
the sins of the Kurozumi Clan.

98
00:05:23.050 --> 00:05:28.600
I am unworthy to even look Lord Sukiyaki
and Lord Oden in the eye!

99
00:05:29.060 --> 00:05:32.770
To compensate for
the follies of my grandfather,

100
00:05:32.770 --> 00:05:38.530
I will assist Lord Oden's enthronement
to the best of my ability!

101
00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:46.830
I shall be your willing puppet
until Lord Oden returns,

102
00:05:46.830 --> 00:05:50.160
so I must ask for everyone's support!

103
00:05:50.790 --> 00:05:52.460
So you're a Kurozumi...

104
00:05:52.460 --> 00:05:54.210
Why didn't you tell me?

105
00:05:54.210 --> 00:05:56.090
Oh, my apologies!

106
00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:03.050
My apologies...!

107
00:06:15.350 --> 00:06:16.650
I can see it!

108
00:06:16.650 --> 00:06:18.270
I can see the future!

109
00:06:19.190 --> 00:06:21.070
You'll...

110
00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:28.450
become shogun!

111
00:06:34.250 --> 00:06:35.960
You scared me, old hag!

112
00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:37.500
Who the hell are you?!

113
00:06:41.170 --> 00:06:44.840
Are you unaware of what happened
to your grandfather?

114
00:06:45.640 --> 00:06:49.850
I don't know all the details,
but I heard he committed seppuku.

115
00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:53.560
Wrong! It was the Kozuki Clan that killed him!

116
00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:54.310
What?!

117
00:06:54.310 --> 00:06:56.770
But I heard he committed some kind of crime!

118
00:06:56.770 --> 00:06:59.820
Engaging in a power struggle isn't a crime!

119
00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:02.440
It was... a power struggle?

120
00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:05.490
If you take the reins, you can make the laws!

121
00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:08.820
You decide what's a crime and what isn't!

122
00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:15.750
The previous shogun from the Kozuki Clan...
was unable to sire any children!

123
00:07:15.750 --> 00:07:17.580
He had no heirs!

