460
00:22:47.220 --> 00:22:50.430
But our celebration
was cut short, as we realized...

461
00:22:51.060 --> 00:22:53.980
that it wasn't the final island!

462
00:22:54.690 --> 00:22:59.860
The needles on the log pose just kept
spinning and wouldn't lock on to anything!

463
00:22:59.860 --> 00:23:02.240
I was convinced.

464
00:23:02.240 --> 00:23:04.820
There had to be one more island!

465
00:23:04.820 --> 00:23:11.700
When I make it there, I'll be the first person
ever to travel all around the world!

466
00:23:12.330 --> 00:23:19.040
And the location of said island is hidden
in the script of these four red stones!

467
00:23:19.880 --> 00:23:26.130
But the World Government has always
forbidden anyone from deciphering them.

468
00:23:26.550 --> 00:23:29.220
They're called poneglyphs.

469
00:23:30.010 --> 00:23:33.100
